    <item>
      <title>韩国推出新制度导致尾盘交易韩元流动性下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/won-liquidity-drops-for-late-trades-as-korea-debuts-new-regime</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在韩元延长交易的第一周深夜时段，韩元的流动性出现下降，这对那些热衷于提振市场的官员来说是一个潜在挫折，并且在全球投资者获得更多渠道之际，加大了价格大幅波动的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/won-liquidity-drops-for-late-trades-as-korea-debuts-new-regime</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:12:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国财报季丰收是股市创下新高的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/a-bumper-us-earnings-season-is-key-for-stocks-to-scale-new-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些华尔街策略师表示，美国企业需要在季度财报季中实现强劲增长，才能延续美国股市破纪录的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/a-bumper-us-earnings-season-is-key-for-stocks-to-scale-new-highs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
